long_description: rubinov's barber and luxury men's shaving supplies store is a full-service family owned and operated business that was established in 2001 in phoenix, arizona. owner and entrepenuer joseph rubinov, an experienced master barber of over 15 years, sought out to create the ultimate one-stop shop for all professional and consumer haircare needs. rubinov's supplies local and nationwide barber shops and beauty shops, barber schools, professionals, as well as many other institutions with a large variety of professional tools and products. rubinov's also specializes in bringing fine classic shaving supplies from all over the world including italy, germany, united states, england, france, spain, canada and russia. professional clipper and latherizer repair as well as scissor and blade sharpening are all available onsite. rubinov's barber supplies llc.
